citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:20 AM on
04/02/2025
Attempted to contact licensee by phone and left message, text, honking horn several times and knocking on residence
and kennel doors. No facility personnel available for inspection.
End Section
